                tại <a href="#" target="_blank"
                    style="color: #00d5ff; text-decoration:underline;">Duckie Store
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; text-align: center; color: #999999; font-size: 14px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">&copy; DuckieStore. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
